cButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2528365\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2528365\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">März 15, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104htp1665702716758.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/htp1665702716758.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/htp1665702716758.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"htp1665702716758\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Execute SQL statement. </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"htp1665702716758__section_N10019_N10016_N10001\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d700673e50\">Modes</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"htp1665702716758__li_d52904e1_d52905e1_d52906e1\">Mode 0—sends a statement in the native DML to the\n               DBMS. If the statement selects data from the database, this mode passes the first\n               field of the last row of the result table to Uniface.</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"htp1665702716758__li_d52907e1_d52908e1_d52909e1\">Mode 2—sends a statement in the native DML to the\n               DBMS. If the statement selects data from the database (for example, SELECT in SQL),\n               this formats the result table according to a Uniface convention. This mode passes the\n               first set of result rows to Uniface.</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"htp1665702716758__li_d52910e1_d52911e1_d52912e1\">Mode 3—passes a subsequent set of result rows to\n               Uniface.</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"htp1665702716758__section_N10035_N10016_N10001\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d700673e68\">Conditions</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"htp1665702716758__d6725e20\">None.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"htp1665702716758__section_N1003A_N10016_N10001\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d700673e77\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"htp1665702716758__p_d152396e1_d152397e1_d152398e1\">This request sends DML statements to the DBMS and is not only for SQL. It is used with the SQL Edit form, for example, and the <code class=\"ph codeph\">sql</code> ProcScript statement. Not supported for all DBMSs.</p>\n<div class=\"div\">Refer to:  <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"zge1665702663349.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zge1665702663349.html\" title=\"Uniface allows you to access data in multiple DBMSs in a uniform way, simultaneously. The term DBMS is used generically here to describe any structured form of data storage that Uniface understands. According to this definition, a record management system is also a DBMS. All the actions carried out on database tables or files occur via the DBMS interface.\">Uniface Database I/O</a>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528365\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528365\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Q Sql Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated März 15, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Execute SQL statement. Modes Mode 0—sends a statement in the native DML to the DBMS. If the statement selects data from the database, this mode passes the first field of the last row of the result table to Uniface. Mode 2—sends a statement in the native DML to the DBMS. If the statement selects data from the database (for example, SELECT in SQL), this formats the result table according to a Uniface convention. This mode passes the first set of result rows to Uniface. Mode 3—passes a subsequent set of result rows to Uniface. Conditions None. Description This request sends DML statements to the DBMS and is not only for SQL. It is used with the SQL Edit form, for example, and the sql ProcScript statement. Not supported for all DBMSs. Refer to: Uniface Database I/O Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}